        {"element": ["code", true, [], [{"text": "@[congr]"}]]},
        {"text": "), reflexivity rules (tagged with "},
        {"element": ["code", true, [], [{"text": "@[refl]"}]]},
        {"text": ") and proof discharging strategies. The full"},
